      <TextArea fx:id="manualTextArea" editable="false" layoutX="40.0" layoutY="100.0" prefHeight="359.0" prefWidth="611.0" text="Bus Terminal User Manual&#10;1. Introduction&#10;1.1 Purpose&#10;Purpose: Welcome to our Bus Terminal User Manual! This comprehensive guide is crafted to empower passengers with a complete understanding of our bus terminal's services and facilities.&#10;&#10;1.2 Audience&#10;Audience: Whether you are a seasoned traveler or a first-time visitor, this manual is designed to cater to all passengers utilizing our bus terminal facilities.&#10;&#10;1.3 Scope&#10;Scope: From booking tickets to arrival procedures, this manual covers every aspect of the passenger journey, providing detailed insights and instructions for a seamless experience.&#10;&#10;2. Getting Started&#10;2.1 Terminal Layout&#10;Terminal Layout: Explore our well-designed terminal layout to easily locate essential services. Find ticketing counters, departure and arrival gates, information desks, restrooms, and other amenities for a hassle-free journey.&#10;&#10;2.2 Ticketing Counters&#10;Ticketing Counters: Conveniently situated throughout the terminal, our ticketing counters offer various booking options. Whether you prefer online reservations or in-person transactions, our counters are here to serve you.&#10;&#10;2.3 Departure and Arrival Gates&#10;Departure and Arrival Gates: Stay informed about the location of departure and arrival gates. Clear signage and regular announcements will guide you through the boarding process with ease.&#10;&#10;2.4 Information Desks&#10;Information Desks: Our friendly staff at information desks are ready to assist you. Whether you need directions, have questions about your journey, or require additional information, feel free to approach our dedicated service points.&#10;&#10;3. Booking Tickets&#10;3.1 Online Booking&#10;Online Booking: Embrace the convenience of online booking through our website or mobile app. Follow our user-friendly interface 